caption.p: Liver, spleen, brain and lung were examined for virus in IHC (A) and histopathology (B). The organs of each mouse were evaluated according to a score between 0 and 3. Scores of each group were presented in a box plot diagram. Significance was analyzed by ANOVA (Kruskal-Wallis H) test (*p<0.05).
